and Terrence Rourke

36:17.686 --> 36:19.287
at the Chateau Hotel.

36:19.354 --> 36:21.953
In other words,
these two tapes were made

36:22.020 --> 36:24.320
by the exact same camera, Jenny.

36:24.387 --> 36:25.853
 <i>Your</i> camera.

36:25.920 --> 36:27.770
Would you please explain
to this jury why you lied

36:27.790 --> 36:30.120
about whose
camera was used
to make the tape ?

36:30.187 --> 36:32.820
I didn't lie. I... I guess
Terry used my camera.

36:32.830 --> 36:34.154
That's not what you said.

36:34.220 --> 36:36.020
You said,
"He showed me his camera.

36:36.087 --> 36:37.553
He must have brought it
with him."

36:37.620 --> 36:38.887
Your testimony is on record.

36:38.953 --> 36:40.154
Shall I have it read back ?

36:40.220 --> 36:41.320
A brief recess,
Your Honor ?

36:41.387 --> 36:42.720
Denied.

36:42.787 --> 36:44.753
Ms. Dennison, would
you please tell this jury

36:44.820 --> 36:47.388
why you videotaped yourself
and Terrence Rourke

36:47.388 --> 36:49.920
having sex at the Chateau Hotel ?

36:49.987 --> 36:53.423
It was all
a big misunderstanding.

36:53.423 --> 36:54.153
Did you tell Terrence

36:54.153 --> 36:55.686
you were videotaping
your sexual encounter ?

36:55.753 --> 36:56.787
No, but...
Why not ?

36:56.853 --> 36:58.254
I didn't think he'd care.

36:58.320 --> 37:00.487
But he did care, did he not ?
In fact, he was horrified

37:00.553 --> 37:02.154
by what you did.
What happened

37:02.220 --> 37:04.686
when Terrence Rourke realized
what you were up to ?

37:04.753 --> 37:08.087
When Terry spotted the camera,
he got really mad.

37:08.154 --> 37:10.553
He was scared
his mom would see the tape.

37:10.620 --> 37:12.403
STARK:
Because you intended
to make the tape public.

37:12.470 --> 37:13.668
I didn't say that !

37:13.668 --> 37:15.120
Is it humanly possible

37:15.187 --> 37:16.887
that you could
have released this tape

37:16.953 --> 37:19.313
to cause a scandal
that would launch your career ?

37:19.313 --> 37:20.521
No.
You didn't
give the tape

37:20.586 --> 37:21.514
to the police.

37:21.514 --> 37:23.154
You took your bloody
little fingers,

37:23.220 --> 37:24.820
walked down the hall,
and slipped it to your manager.

37:24.887 --> 37:28.586
And now it somehow magically--
miracle of miracles--

37:28.653 --> 37:30.521
finds its way onto the Internet.

37:30.586 --> 37:33.553
Now everybody's
talking about it--
talking about you--

37:33.620 --> 37:36.820
the week your first album
is about to be released.

37:36.887 --> 37:38.320
Can you look this
jury in the eye

37:38.387 --> 37:40.387
and tell any
single one of
them that this is

37:40.454 --> 37:41.653
a cosmic accident ?

37:45.553 --> 37:50.787
Now, would you
kindly tell this jury

37:50.853 --> 37:53.254
what happened
in that hotel room

37:53.320 --> 37:55.154
between you

37:55.220 --> 37:56.753
and Terrence Rourke ?

37:56.820 --> 38:02.454
Terry tried to grab the tape.

38:02.521 --> 38:04.318
He wrestled me
onto the bed,

38:04.318 --> 38:07.586
his knee was on my chest.

38:07.653 --> 38:09.553
I should have just
given it to him.

38:09.620 --> 38:10.787
STARK:
Why didn't you ?

38:10.853 --> 38:12.787
I don't know.

38:12.853 --> 38:15.387
I couldn't breathe.

38:15.454 --> 38:18.553
I got scared.
I was still kind of drunk.

38:18.620 --> 38:19.953
When I grabbed the knife,

38:20.020 --> 38:23.020
I just wanted to scare him,
to make him stop.

38:23.087 --> 38:25.254
I don't know
how this all happened.

38:25.320 --> 38:28.287
STARK:
Jenny, you do,
because the moment

38:28.354 --> 38:29.620
you met Terrence Rourke,

38:29.686 --> 38:32.487
you decided to videotape
your sexual encounter.

38:32.553 --> 38:35.586
That part was premeditated,
was it not ?

38:35.653 --> 38:39.553
Yes, but I swear to God,
I never meant to hurt him.

38:39.620 --> 38:40.887
Please believe me.

38:42.987 --> 38:45.887
I do.

38:45.953 --> 38:50.820
But your plan
cost him his life.

38:50.887 --> 38:54.120
It cost Elizabeth Rourke

38:54.187 --> 38:56.254
her only child.

38:56.320 --> 38:58.720
There is
no greater loss.

39:00.020 --> 39:02.953
No further questions,
Your Honor.

39:05.686 --> 39:08.787
Hi.
Let me get a photo
with the man of the hour.

39:08.853 --> 39:09.595
Your Honor.

39:09.595 --> 39:11.920
 Madam District Attorney,
 <i>por favor.</i>

39:16.987 --> 39:18.087
Beginner's
luck.

39:18.154 --> 39:19.454
It's called winning.
One more ?

39:19.521 --> 39:21.354
Don't worry--
you'll get used to it.

39:21.421 --> 39:22.987
That's good.
Thank you,
Your Honor.

39:23.054 --> 39:23.891
Thanks, Manny.

39:23.891 --> 39:28.387
I am going to
give you exactly 30
seconds to gloat.

39:29.365 --> 39:32.386
Hey, you-you do
know you just won
a huge case, right ?

39:32.386 --> 39:32.878
Yeah.

39:32.878 --> 39:34.295
You look like you just
lost your best friend.

39:34.295 --> 39:38.287
I'm about to lose a hell
of a lot more than that.

39:38.354 --> 39:40.553
As stipulated in your
parents' divorce decree,

39:40.620 --> 39:42.067
having reached
the age of 16,

39:42.087 --> 39:43.379
you must now
designate

39:43.379 --> 39:45.187
which parent will
act as custodian

39:45.254 --> 39:46.720
until your
18th birthday.

39:46.787 --> 39:48.320
Have you reached
a decision ?

39:53.220 --> 39:55.487
Yes.

39:55.553 --> 39:57.920
My mother's been everything
to me.

39:57.987 --> 40:00.920
My protector, my best friend.

40:00.987 --> 40:03.087
When my parents got a divorce,

40:03.154 --> 40:05.586
I thought the world was coming
to an end.

40:05.653 --> 40:08.020
But she made sure it didn't.

40:08.087 --> 40:09.653
I mean, she was a mess,

40:09.720 --> 40:12.454
but she pretended
like everything was okay

40:12.521 --> 40:15.853
so that I wouldn't be scared.

40:15.920 --> 40:19.920
And it wasn't always easy.

40:19.987 --> 40:22.487
I can be a real pain.

40:22.553 --> 40:27.020
But my mom taught me
that it's not enough

40:27.087 --> 40:28.787
to love someone when it's easy.

40:28.853 --> 40:31.653
You got to love
them when it's hard.

40:31.720 --> 40:35.686
When they don't deserve it,
when they're in trouble.

40:35.753 --> 40:39.421
That's what family does.

40:43.354 --> 40:46.087
Which is why I choose
to live with my dad.

40:53.255 --> 40:54.210
 ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ?

40:54.220 --> 40:56.320
I'm as surprised
as you are, probably more.

40:57.686 --> 40:59.713
I didn't mean
to hurt you.

40:59.713 --> 41:00.887
Oh, I'm not hurt.

41:01.028 --> 41:04.262
Well, okay,
I'm a little hurt,

41:04.272 --> 41:05.748
but mostly
I'm scared.

41:05.748 --> 41:07.248
I mean, no offense,
Sebastian,

41:07.314 --> 41:10.312
but you are incredibly
self-absorbed.

41:10.312 --> 41:11.157
No offense taken.

41:11.057 --> 41:12.988
Well, seriously, do you have
any idea what it takes

41:12.988 --> 41:14.855
to raise a teenage girl
alone in Los Angeles ?

41:14.921 --> 41:17.167
No, but if this is
what Julie wants, I...

41:17.177 --> 41:19.222
What she wants !
She's 16 !

41:19.287 --> 41:22.032
She wants a Porsche,
a date with Prince William,

41:22.032 --> 41:23.017
and world peace.

41:23.017 --> 41:24.119
Uh, Mom...
She's a child.

41:24.119 --> 41:28.122
My whole
life is here.

41:28.481 --> 41:29.355
Oh, Jules.

41:32.287 --> 41:34.390
If this is really
what you want...

41:34.390 --> 41:38.354
...I can't stop you.

41:38.421 --> 41:41.788
I just hope to God
you know what you're doing.

41:43.155 --> 41:46.421
This is the biggest case
you'll ever get.

41:48.122 --> 41:50.287
Don't blow it.

42:04.387 --> 42:06.654
Why ?

42:06.721 --> 42:10.122
You're the only father
I'm ever going to have,

42:10.188 --> 42:12.421
and, if there is a God,

42:12.488 --> 42:15.088
I'm the only kid
you're ever going to have.

42:15.155 --> 42:19.721
Mom's really mad right now,
but she'll get over it.

42:19.788 --> 42:22.188
If I go to New York,

42:22.254 --> 42:26.671
you and I will exchange
birthday cards

42:26.671 --> 42:27.993
and Christmas presents,

42:27.993 --> 42:32.821
but we'll wind up
perfect strangers.

42:32.888 --> 42:35.472
You may prefer that,
but I don't.

42:35.472 --> 42:36.678
The last thing
I would ever want...

42:36.678 --> 42:39.554
For once, don't say anything.

42:39.621 --> 42:41.721
I've gone to the shrink
long enough to know

42:41.788 --> 42:43.521
that I'll be screwed up for life

42:43.588 --> 42:46.188
if I don't get some closure
on you and me.

42:46.254 --> 42:50.588
And there's another reason
why I chose you.

42:50.654 --> 42:53.721
Something you probably
don't understand,

42:53.788 --> 42:56.321
and maybe you never will.

42:57.988 --> 43:00.188
You need me.

